        <div class="bg-surface rounded-2xl p-6 border border-outline/10 text-on-surface-variant">Use one bullet list for the options.</div>
        <div class="bg-surface rounded-2xl p-6 border border-outline/10 text-on-surface-variant">Write answer and explanation as labeled paragraphs